data.description: WELCOME TO THE COMMUNITY OF PARADISE BEACH!  A gem of a hidden community on the Chesapeake Bay!  Chesapeake Schools!  This home is located 1.5 blocks from the community beach.  Move-in ready and situated on almost 1/2 an acre!   Features: Primary Bedroom with 2 Closets and a Primary Bath.  The Open Floor Plan features a Kitchen with an Island, Pantry, and Stainless Appliances and is loaded with windows and natural daylight.  A sliding Door in the Dining Area opens to an Oversized Deck overlooking the serene backyard and pool.  The lower level features a Family Room w/Wood Stove, 4th Bedroom, and an Unfinished Bath with rough In.  Added extras in the lower level are the Den that can be used as Office Space and Play Room.  A separate Finished Laundry room is located just off the family room.   Unfinished Bath with Rough In.  The garage is the PERFECT MANCAVE and has access from the Family Room Level and features a Sliding Glass door to walk out to the backyard and onto an OVERSIZED Concrete Patio, shaded by the Upper Deck and Trees.  Paradise Beach is a great WALKING COMMUNITY that features a VOLUNTARY PARADISE BEACH IMPROVEMENT ASSOCIATION that enjoys many community activities, a community beach, and a community lot where many community functions are enjoyed by all!  Don't Miss This One!
